00vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">2025年英国颁奖典礼</a>于今晚（3月1日）在伦敦举行 - 请参阅下面的获奖者的完整列表。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="974" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514"><b>这是2025年英国奖的所有提名人</b></a></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>以五个点头提名进入了深夜，在一个令人印象深刻的夜晚，她获得了四个奖项。她赢得了年度最佳专辑，年度艺术家和舞蹈表演，以及与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>的合作“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-billie-eilish-guess-remix-the-dare-finneas-3780251">Guess”</a> ，获得了年度最佳歌曲奖。她也已经被任命为“年度词曲作者奖”奖。</p><p>仪式在O2举行，在ITV1和ITVX上现场直播，喜剧演员和演员 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-jack-whitehall-to-return-as-host-3829454">杰克·怀特霍尔（Jack Whitehall）自2021年以来首次返回演出</a>，总体上是第五次。 </p><figure id="attachment_3814654" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3814654" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3814654" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/BRITS@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2025英国奖奖杯由加布里埃尔·摩西（Gabriel Moses）设计" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/BRITS@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/BRITS@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/BRITS@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/BRITS@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/BRITS@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/BRITS@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3814654" class="wp-caption-text"> 2025年，由加布里埃尔·摩西（Gabriel Moses）设计的英国奖奖杯。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3842602" aria-describedby="caption-attachment